{"id":"29b52bfcccd01518e9de561ca2e3eb7833293506f0ed0743ae2b83a1a8ee7351","item_id":"83c5148157:0","text":"Smoke（烟雾）"}
{"id":"087a4af5ded6c77f0469e67321a1fd1f889bf2a099eb13bf0ac07b20ec7689fc","item_id":"83c5148157:1","text":"Smoke Volume（烟雾体积）"}
{"id":"79e7d1dd628afc0904f19ceae0cf7e955e0f4b1e6e25f696e96b06f3a9ba67ad","item_id":"83c5148157:2","text":"用于渲染预期密度的必需 string field（字符串字段）。应始终指定一个 float field（浮点字段）。该字段用于 PxrVolume shader 的 Density Float 参数。"}
{"id":"4720c0c3df2ea08e01c790276dc47b5258c4b693f6e9be8a88149a1b2c880010","item_id":"83c5148157:3","text":"Scatter（散射）"}
{"id":"b653934bf899d374b3089e7c35de8b351cbdb0c25e51a7982704badb32d207b0","item_id":"83c5148157:4","text":"Source Volume（源体积）"}
{"id":"d02a5bb289ecb3a9797f6f7b50afcbe086110fb9cc34e72597267f4f4928bff0","item_id":"83c5148157:5","text":"用于生成 scatter data（散射数据）的字段。"}
{"id":"5bbba6604b35d82f654dccc3d03dd91970ad0baa0496fb5c445682cc989a1e3a","item_id":"83c5148157:6","text":"Mask Volume（遮罩体积）"}
{"id":"170b67767d7d98481633e7015ca986bd238bf3e58eeb0e5b23136ee3cb8c7073","item_id":"83c5148157:7","text":"用于生成 multiplier（乘数）的字段，以控制由 Scatter Source Volume 生成的 scatter data 的作用范围。"}
{"id":"1b8d02c71de5c0d3723437c76fe501bd53af018c35762683cc0c8d6b6b1708ee","item_id":"83c5148157:8","text":"Scatter Volume（散射体积）"}
{"id":"f781b6d6be31fd20158bc2b9837f818fd9921ac683dedd4c30144a9969cd5dcf","item_id":"83c5148157:9","text":"用于写入 scatter 结果的必需 string field。"}
{"id":"c141faa80e43a11909f5736d1e767f12e1468aa06dadd446081746934e875fc3","item_id":"83c5148157:10","text":"Fire（火焰）"}
{"id":"c7f04806b3ddeeaafc4c72b226dd58aac5ece0fad355e660e29541bad7dda2a0","item_id":"83c5148157:11","text":"Intensity Volume（强度体积）"}
{"id":"34e1a36585ce0b20c21c96e28191fdbeeec1503cead8d9abd7719b5da210c21f","item_id":"83c5148157:12","text":"用于为 Diffuse Color Volume 和 Emit Color Volume 生成 base color（基础颜色）与 intensity（强度）值的字段。"}
{"id":"f8e1ad8092b4d2242958eae14df375c669359b26b22c5bdd5823ca0a0d1118c7","item_id":"83c5148157:13","text":"Flame Volume（火焰体积）"}
{"id":"ff17d869e4e244acbc7e035d906d8cc9da4ac8a02a48dd80c2fc47fe71b5de87","item_id":"83c5148157:14","text":"配合 Fire 选项卡中的 Fire Mask 选项，用于定义来自 Intensity Volume 的颜色和强度数据的应用区域。当 Smoke 被禁用时，也会用于替代 density float（密度浮点）值。"}
{"id":"6b73191a0a4b67420e61d51c9f207c35277eaf18fbbf5beb52a320a23fe09653","item_id":"83c5148157:15","text":"Color（颜色）"}
{"id":"86fdaea04912745263b5c0fada37bfbabc86103a3674d8341e3b14f6c0bf5fbf","item_id":"83c5148157:16","text":"Diffuse Color Volume（漫反射颜色体积）"}
{"id":"b6cda72fde3cc9ed8c3f3ff32eedf3a8e035c277e0faf6f7712262b5638481eb","item_id":"83c5148157:17","text":"必需的 string field，用于让 pyro 使用用户设计的颜色进行渲染，而不是非默认颜色 (1,1,1)。该字段用于 PxrVolume shader 的 Diffuse Color 参数。"}
{"id":"2b6e10ebed50dbabcc0ed1d216b8e7a633eba02298fd96558a86202b406052aa","item_id":"83c5148157:18","text":"Emit Color Volume（发射颜色体积）"}
{"id":"60aa422b6ab218d6dfec0040e19b01f62c21341d49839eae89b6fe393f45df29","item_id":"83c5148157:19","text":"必需的 string field，用于让 pyro 使用用户设计的颜色进行渲染，而不是非默认颜色 (0,0,0)。该字段用于 PxrVolume shader 的 Emission Color 参数。"}
{"id":"6d89eb7d0938564938636b4a5ee73c09e55c2e6e5aaa9e3016781bf54805e8d3","item_id":"83c5148157:20","text":"Render（渲染）"}
{"id":"459fbc80c087cc386cc30feb4a61e18a34ac95b6e02d3f4fd5e08fd4d1afec0d","item_id":"83c5148157:21","text":"Velocity Volume（速度体积）"}
{"id":"41ab5fc147315a4fec620212b8ae5c76b50d5f0469a93796e10bc1c1e1277692","item_id":"83c5148157:22","text":"必需的 string field，用于使用模拟生成的 velocities（速度）进行运动，而不是默认值 (0,0,0)，或用户在 Render 选项卡中指定的 uniform direction（统一方向）。空 string field 会在 Render 选项卡中显示 uniform direction velocity 参数。"}
{"id":"c2fa450197e1c2ae51fabb7a895d601e75b0707349733dacca898dafe07eece0","item_id":"83c5148157:23","text":"该字段用于 PxrVolume shader 的 Velocity 参数。"}
